title: Playable ART Ball Game
description:
The perfect game for the aspiring architect both young and old!                                                               
Our game features twenty multi-colored interconnected spheres that can be turned, twisted, and scrunched into an endless array of elegant configurations.  Made from beech wood,  and dyed with non-toxic, water-based paint.  

1 1/4 in. diam.

Recommended for ages 3 yrs and up.
